issue.title: API Key Authentication
issue.body: In order to discourage api abuse and increase accountability, as well as to enhance security and privacy, as an api consumer, I should not have access to an API response unless I first register for a developer account and specify my`api_key` in my api  request.

issue.title: Format appear_time in api response
issue.body: The current formatting of `appear_time` is "2000-01-01 14:00:00 UTC" but needs to only be "14:00"

issue.title: Court Location Code Lookup Table
issue.body:
Included in vine files is a `locn_code` attribute which identifies a court. The problem is we don't know the corresponding court names for each code.

As an API consumer, in order to know the court to which I need to appear, I should be able to see this information returned as part of the `event_search` api response.
